-- Sinochem, Uralkali Fail to Agree on Possible Potash Bid, FT Says
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 2010-09-29T22:22:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-29/sinochem-group-uralkali-fail-to-agree-on-possible-potash-bid-ft-reports.html
Sinochem Group’s talks with OAO
Uralkali about forming a group to make a bid for Potash Corp. of
Saskatchewan Inc. collapsed last week, the Financial Times
reported, citing three people close to the talks that it didn’t
identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
